title: Connecting the LOOΠΔVERSE: LOOΠΔ 1/3 (Love&Live) #3
body:
Specific  Connections

First off, I would like to point out that the beginning shots of Love&Live parallel the opening shots of My Sunday and My Melody

Looking through a chainlink fence

Connects to: Girl Front (Odd Eye Circle), new (Yves)

Strange eye

Connects to: Odd Eye Circle

Sitting on top of a roof thing

Connects to: Let Me In (Haseul), new (Yves)

Looking at the other members from far-off through a window

Connects to: The Carol (Heejin, Hyunjin, Haseul), Heart Attack (Chuu)

Falling asleep

Connects to: Love Cherry Motion (Choerry)

The iconic Look

Connects to: Girl Front (Odd Eye Circle)

Running (legs)

Connects to: Singing in the Rain (Jinsoul), Love Cherry Motion (Choerry), Girl Front (Odd Eye Circle), Sweet Crazy Love (Odd Eye Circle), One & Only (Gowon)

Running (from the back)

Connects to: Love Cherry Motion (Choerry)

The final member of each subunit is a link to the others.  Just like how Choerry visits OEC when she ‘sleeps’, I belive Vivi visits the final subunit when she sleeps.

It’s also noteable how similar the running shot with Vivi is to the shot with Choerry in LCM.  They’re both runnig from the back, with colored hair, white shirts, short shorts, long socks and white sneakers.

caption:
[Chuu (Loona) - Heart Attack] I love their concept presenting each member with a solo song, but this is just the second song I like

“ The day we first met,
inside my quiet heart
As if a new world has opened
Accelerate particularly, move
Even my hidden secrets that only i knew
That mood that i wanted to tell you all about”
